Notes

  1. ↑ 1.0 1.1 File/folder structure within this directory reflects the path(s) listed for Windows and/or Steam game data (use Wine regedit to access Windows registry paths). Games with Steam Cloud support may store data in ~/.steam/steam/userdata/<user-id>/869690/ in addition to or instead of this directory. The app ID (869690) may differ in some cases. Treat backslashes as forward slashes. See the glossary page for details.
